SET @Period1 = 1;
SET @Period2 = 2;
SET @Period3 = 5;
SET @Base1 = @Period1 * 365 * 24 * 60 * 60;
SET @Base2 = @Period2 * 365 * 24 * 60 * 60;
SET @Base3 = @Period3 * 365 * 24 * 60 * 60;
SELECT
parentPath as "Path",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime >= NOW() - @Base1 THEN 1
ELSE 0
END) AS "Count 1 year or newer",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime >= NOW() - @Base1 THEN size
ELSE 0
END) AS "Size 1 year or newer",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime >= NOW() - @Base2 AND modifyTime < NOW() - @Base1 THEN 1
ELSE 0
END) AS "Count 1 to 2 years old",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime >= NOW() - @Base2 AND modifyTime < NOW() - @Base1 THEN size
ELSE 0
END) AS "Size 1 to 2 years old",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime >= NOW() - @Base3 AND modifyTime < NOW() - @Base2 THEN 1
ELSE 0
END) AS "Count 2 to 5 years old",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime >= NOW() - @Base3 AND modifyTime < NOW() - @Base2 THEN size
ELSE 0
END) AS "Size 2 to 5 years old",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime < NOW() - @Base3 THEN 1
ELSE 0
END) AS "Count Older than 5 years",
SUM(CASE
WHEN modifyTime < NOW() - @Base3 THEN size
ELSE 0
END) AS "Size Older than 5 years",
SUM(size) AS "Total Size"
GROUP BY
parentPath

  COMPONENTS(parentPath, 9) AS Subfolder,
  SUM(size) as "Size",
  COUNT(name) as "Count"

WHERE ClassID LIKE 'idxobject'

GROUP BY Subfolder

ORDER BY SUM(size) Desc
